{"tid":1772571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"230磅細細粒 挑戰空中瑜伽","createTime":"2019-12-06T17:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T17:50:16.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"88035bcb37c387453f194ee5f95cbd3ac7f8c031","tid":1772571,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2510000/2514058/20191206JLD003__20191206_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2510000%2F2514058%2F20191206JLD003__20191206_L.jpg&h=6dfa6d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳嘉佳（細細粒）早前為響應「邁向2025︰香港非傳染病防控策略及行動計劃」，拍攝健康教育宣傳短片。為了令宣傳片更有趣，自誇有高溫瑜伽經驗的細細粒，特意在鏡頭前越級挑戰空中瑜伽。<br />\n<br />\n不過體重高達230磅的她，上繩動作已相當吃力，多次露出超誇張的痛苦及驚嚇表情，令工作人員笑破肚皮，幸好最後順利完成拍攝。事後細細粒自爆放棄做高溫瑜伽的原因︰「因為上堂我覺得好舒服，有幾次做做下瞓着咗，感覺好似好浪費咁，所以無再去喇！」"},{"pid":"c6ed00706aa2755303d27dc799eb395f8c2ede87","tid":1772571,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Jjg-VoAPhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Jjg-VoAPhM&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9a2baaba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Jjg-VoAPhM</a><br />\n😵"},{"pid":"e6f4d96dc0fa46d4ee06915378b9b9189ea10df6","tid":1772571,"uid":185092,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"條帶好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b8d2d672aea2c559dfa6d37e921498db9bb872","tid":1772571,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"藍"},{"pid":"ddcc88d511da355817068b4b2a3d235c790037b1","tid":1772571,"uid":73862,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"無人想知<br />\n<br />\n128 見"},{"pid":"77ffc0bfc52959526bf14747d152b0fbdd8dcf6b","tid